posts.subject: Promised chan
posts.body: I just want to do Kek's will. And He's allowed me to go up to the mountain. And I've looked over. And I've seen the Promised Chan. I may not get there with you. But I want you to know tonight, that we, as a people, will get to the Promised Chan. So I'm happy, tonight. I'm not worried about anything. I'm not fearing any man. Mine eyes have seen the glory of the coming of the memes.
I don't know anything really but I've always taken the view that if you eat plenty of variety you're probably not going to go too far wrong. So I try to eat as much different stuff as possible.
